															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250341" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;" >Agent MacLeod</a></span> <span class="odate time_1435312688 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">26 Jun 2015 09:58</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2325366">
									

<p>Too many people to thank. Just, like, reply here to take credit.</p>
<p>This is meant to have five chapters; the remaining three will be added on the same way entries were added on to <a href="/incursion">Incursion</a> over an extended period. However, these two are both meant to be complementary standalones, as are the subsequent chapters.</p>
<p>I hope you folks enjoy reading it!</p>
<p>EDIT: Quick disclaimer that I should have made when I first posted this story: at points, this story deals with racial tension and outright racism; characters within this story explicitly use derogatory language and racial slurs. The opinions of these fictitious characters do not reflect my own opinions in any capacity and it is my intention that invocation of such provocative imagery positively impacts the narrative and provides insight into the characters expressing these negative opinions. I understand that it's an immensely sensitive issue and I hope it was handled in a way that is understandable</p>

							</div>

								
